snippet.title: What a way to start the Equiverse journey! - Devlog #1
snippet.description:
Discord: https://discord.gg/hay2fMBggT

Join me as I dive into the development journey of Equiverse! From designing satisfying gameplay loops to battling monsters and crafting a vibrant ecosystem, I’ll share the highs, the lows, and everything in between. Plus, get a sneak peek at my future plans and challenges. Don’t miss out on this exciting dev log adventure! 

Credits:
Music is not mine and is from the show Pat & Mat
Footage used from Insaniquarium, Cookie Clicker and Luxor HD
